    "Real-time analytics are essential for providing immediate feedback and adjustments in animation design.",
    "The architectures of edge intelligence systems are typically layered, comprising the edge layer (where data is generated and initially processed), the fog layer (which provides additional processing and storage capabilities), and the cloud layer (for more extensive processing and long-term storage).",
